headline: 2 Reasons to Watch CSGP and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: CoStar currently trades at $76.71 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a small loss of 3.2%. However, the stock is beating the S&P 500’s 10% decline during that period.
